{"id":46214,"date":"2021-09-17T10:06:00","date_gmt":"2021-09-17T09:06:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=46214"},"modified":"2021-10-25T09:14:33","modified_gmt":"2021-10-25T08:14:33","slug":"national-parks-sri-lanka","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/national-parks-sri-lanka\/","title":{"rendered":"The Best National Parks in Sri Lanka for a Safari"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-national-parks-in-sri-lanka\"><strong>National Parks in Sri Lanka<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are over 20 national parks in Sri Lanka, with various landscapes, from open plains, beautiful lakes, bushland, grasslands, and even beaches! Where you go on safari is totally dependant on your personal preference. For example, are you keen to spot the elusive leopard, or do you prefer to see herds of elephants? This will be a factor in deciding which national park to choose from.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12.jpg\" alt=\"National Parks Sri Lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"313\" alt=\"National Parks Sri Lanka\" class=\"wp-image-63893 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-800x557.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-1080x752.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-450x313.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-163x113.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-259x180.jpg 259w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-768x534.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-1024x713.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-1440x1002.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-300x209.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-600x418.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091558\/sri-lanka-national-parks-12.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"besttime\">Best Time to go on Safari<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are two monsoon seasons in Sri Lanka: The northeast monsoon season which takes place from October to January and the southwest monsoon season which takes place from May to July. It&#x2019;s best to avoid these times, as animals will take shelter and be harder to spot during the heavy rains. The dry seasons are an excellent time to visit national parks in Sri Lanka, as the animals come out of cover to search for water.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4.jpg\" alt=\"National Parks Sri Lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"423\" height=\"338\" alt=\"National Parks Sri Lanka\" class=\"wp-image-63879 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4-750x600.jpg 750w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4-1013x810.jpg 1013w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4-423x338.jpg 423w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4-30x24.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4-163x130.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4-225x180.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4-1351x1080.jpg 1351w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091442\/sri-lanka-national-parks-4-1801x1440.jpg 1801w, h