the price of visiting a national park in Sri Lanka<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"National Parks Sri Lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"National Parks Sri Lanka\" data-id=\"63885\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=63885\" class=\"wp-image-63885 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/07091515\/sri-lanka-national-parks-8-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/w